## Quick Syntax Reference (xWiki 2.1)
- Headings: `= H1 =`, `== H2 ==`, `=== H3 ===`
- Bold: `**bold**`, Italic: `//italic//`
- Links: `[[Link Text>>Space.Page]]`
- Info boxes: `{{info}}...{{/info}}`, `{{warning}}...{{/warning}}`
- Diagrams: `{{mermaid}}...{{/mermaid}}`
- Code: `{{code language="..."}}...{{/code}}`

## Rules
- Preserve existing syntax when editing.
- Each document lives in ONE authoritative format (`.md` or `.xwiki`, not both).
- Follow terminology from `/AGENTS.md` (AnalysisContext, EvidenceScope, EvidenceItem).
